arenella-app-cookies-text1: Cookies are used for security and to gain the site visitors consent to the terms and conditions. We use cookies for no other purpose
arenella-app-cookies-text2: The site visitor is not tracked by the application and we do not collect statistics for site visitors.
arenella-app-cookies-text3:
We store information about the Recruiters required to identify and contact them. Information about the actions the recruiter performs may be stored to provide insight relating to the 
		individual recruiters use of the site and to help improve the site. The Recruiters information will not be shared with third parties without their explicit consent.
arenella-app-cookies-text4:
Candidates are only added into the system with their consent or via the consent of the company that employs them. The Candidates informaion is available internally in the system and 
		can also be downloaded by the Recruiters in order to contact them about potentially interesting roles. Candidates CVs can also be downloaded by the Recruiters.
arenella-app-cookies-text5-a:
By accepting these Terms and Conditions the recruiter agrees that the use of the site and data accessed via the site are entirely at their own risk. The Recruiter agrees that the Arenella BV is 
		in no way responsible for any negative consequences on them or their company from the use of this site or the data or files contained therin.
arenella-app-cookies-text5-b:
By accepting these terms and conditions the recruiter agrees that the use of the Candidate data is limited to the sole use of contacting the Candidates about potentially relevant jobs 
		that may be of interest to the Candidate. The Candidates data may not be passed on to third parties without the Candidates express permission and may not be stored in the Recruiters own 
		system for longer than necessary to complete the recruitment process for the Candidate they are trying to place.
arenella-app-cookies-text6:
By uploading the CV or providing it to the site the Candidate has aggreed for their CV and information to be shared with the network of Recruiters that are already and will 
		subsequently make use of the website. A Recruiter is any person or conpany with an account on the website that it looking for Candidates to place in a new role. 
		The Candidate agrees that the Recruiters can access all their information contained within the site in order to contact them with potentially relevant job openings. Information will be 
		extracted from within the CV and stored seperately in the site. This information may be made accessible to the Recruiters.
arenella-app-cookies-text7:
Recruiters information will be stored in the System for the duration of their subscriptions. After which their data will either be removed or identifiable references to the Recruiter will be 
		replaced. This update will be periodic but the we will make best endevours to make these updates as quickly as possible.
arenella-app-cookies-text8:
Candidates whose profiles have been accepted will receive login details for their Candidate account. Their account and profile will remain in the system up until the point they delete their profile. 
		Candidates may also email the site administrator and request their details are removed from the site.

The recruiters, IT agencies and Hiring Managers are all independent of the Arenella-ICT platform, making Arenella-ICT a one stop shop for reaching a whole

arenella-faqs-header: IT Candidate CV Database - IT Job board - IT Marketplace
arenella-faqs-q1-answer: By default, when you signup you will have a Credit based subscription with limited weekly downloads. This is 100% free. You can also select a paid subscription, this gives you extra benefits such as unlimited downloads and access to an additional pool of IT candidates.
arenella-faqs-q1-question: Is there a charge for subscription
arenella-faqs-q4-answer: No. There are no margins, commissions or extra costs to pay. If you stick to the credit based subscription there are no costs at all. If you chose the paid subscription the only cost is the subscription itself.
arenella-faqs-q5-answer: The invoice is sent from Arenella BV a Dutch registered company in the Netherlands.
arenella-faqs-q5-question: Where will the invoice for the subscription come from
arenella-faqs-q6-answer: Yes. When you view / download the candidates CV you will see their contact details. You can call them directly.
arenella-faqs-q6-question: Can I contact the candidates directly
arenella-faqs-q7-answer:
Yes. All candidates have either uploaded their CVs themselves via the site with the intention of having them downloaded by recruiters who will call them or have 
								given permission to have them uploaded on their behalf for the same reason. We do not add any CV that has not been expressly provided to us for this purpose.
arenella-faqs-q7-question: Do candidates know their details are being shared
arenella-faqs-q8-answer:
Yes. Candidates availability is checked based upon their LinkedIn status roughly every two weeks. Providing their statuses are up to date the majority of candidates 
								are actively looking for a new role.
arenella-faqs-q9-answer: There are candidates available all over Europe
arenella-faqs-q9-answer-summary: You can filter on candidates that speak the language you are looking for
arenella-faqs-q9-question: What countries are the candidates located in
arenella-faqs-q10-answer: Yes. The candidates are living in the county where they are looking for work and are either nationals of that country or have a valid work visa.
arenella-faqs-q11-answer: The candidates speak a variety of languages. You can filter on the languages that you are interested in to find IT candidates that speak those languages and see their level of fluency in those languages.
arenella-faqs-q11-answer-summary: You can filter on candidates that speak the language you are looking for.
arenella-faqs-q11-question: What languages do the candidates speak
arenella-homepage-candidates-1:
Candidates have either uploaded their CV to the site or have given permission for that to happen, with the
				intention of having recruiters contact them. Our candidates are open to working with recruiters and actively
				looking for a new role via a recruitment agency.
arenella-homepage-candidates-2: We check candidate availability roughly every two weeks to ensure availability based upon their LinkedIn status. Candidate no longer available are removed from the search results. Their status is then checked every two month to determine if they have become available again. We aim to reduce your time spent contacting candidates that are not actively looking for a role. IT Recruiters with a paid subscription also have the option to filter on and contact the unavailable candidates.
arenella-homepage-candidates-3:
We check candidate availability roughly every two weeks to ensure availability based upon their LinkedIn status. Once
a candidate is no longer available they are removed from the search results. Their status is then checked every
two month to determines if they have become available. We aim to reduce the your spent contacting candidates
that are not actively looking for a role.
arenella-homepage-candidates-4: Candidates are based throughout Europe and have the right to work. There are candidates for most types of IT function on both a permanent and freelance basis.
arenella-homepage-fees-1: You will be pleased to hear there are no additional margins or fees for placing a candidate. The only payment is the yearly subscription in the case you opt for a paid, rather than free credit based subscription option.
arenella-homepage-fees-2: Arenella-ICT is a platform and we do not work as a recruitment agency ourselves. Therefore when you place a candidate any contract is between you and the candidate. Arenella-ICT stays out of contracts and negotiations.
arenella-homepage-func-jb-desc: A Job board for advertising roles to candidates both registered and unregistered with the platform
arenella-homepage-func-market-desc: Collaborate with other agencies and clients to fill their open roles or request candidates for your own open roles.
arenella-homepage-func-news-desc: Insight into candidate updates (availability, CV update, profile update)
arenella-homepage-func-suggestions-desc: A CV database with advanced algorithms to find the best candidates in a matter of seconds.
arenella-homepage-getting-started: The first step is to create an account. You will be asked for your name, your email address and company name. You will receive an email with your login details.
arenella-homepage-title-intro-text: Arenella-ICT is a platform for IT recruiters to find immediately available candidates. We provide a suite of functionality, optimized to help you find the best candidates in the shortest time possible.
arenella-homepage-title-pricing-plan-cre: Weekly credit allocation to access site features.
arenella-homepage-title-pricing-plan-pai: Unlimited access to all Recruiter features on the site.

arenella-listing-intro: A place for IT candidates and IT recruiters to come together
arenella-listing-most-searched-summary: The IT recruiters who use Arenella-ICT work for their own recruitment agencies. Each recruiter / recruitment agency has their own roles to fill. Some of the recruiters choose to advertise their open roles on the job board. Others prefer to search on the profiles and contact the candidates directly. The above charts show information relating to the most popular types of candidates over the past 30 days. By creating a free profile, the recruiters will be able to contact you with relevant roles. Recruiters will likely call in the name of their own recruitment agency and not in the name of Arenella-ICT.
